title: Ex-Freedom RB Joe Mixon with Sooners after yearlong benching
text:
Photo: Alonzo Adams, Associated Press Joe Mixon has gained more than 300 yards rushing and receiving for Oklahoma and has scored three touchdowns. Joe Mixon has gained more than 300 yards rushing and receiving for...
Oklahoma redshirt freshman Joe Mixon scored his first college rushing touchdown Saturday, which greatly pleased his former high school coach at Freedom-Oakley.
